ht to alter any course, procedure or fee. Please check for changes before you apply or enrol.</p><p>Federation University uses Victorian and Commonwealth Government funding (for eligible students) to deliver training.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;">School department</p><p>Psychology</p><p style="font-weight: bold;">Course co-ordinator</p><p>Megan Jenkins</p></div></div>',
